6 months ago I got hit by a drunk driver. There wasn’t much between his vehicle and mine, but I do give thanks to my Gritty music binder for putting up a fight, and the NYFD for fishing both him and me out of the wreck. We are both a bit worse for wear, but grateful to be able to carry on.
